Which also doesn't
suck, obviously.

03:48.621 --> 03:51.155
Unlike you
who totally sucks obviously!

03:51.157 --> 03:52.890
Will you shut up?!

03:52.892 --> 03:57.461
I swear to God, if you get us kicked
off before I get my jumbo scrimps on -

03:57.463 --> 03:59.997
You'll wish you were
Michael Findlay.

03:59.999 --> 04:01.632
A, Cecil won't
kick you off, he wants

04:01.634 --> 04:04.101
everybody here, for no good reason--
He doesn't need one,

04:04.103 --> 04:07.705
he's an American hero. Who's
going to make me rich.

04:07.707 --> 04:09.606
And B, that's
not even real shrimp.

04:09.608 --> 04:11.008
This is all vegan-soy-bullshit.

04:11.010 --> 04:12.042
Pffrrfft! Prrfft! Puh!

04:12.044 --> 04:14.077
Because he's
totally vegan, because his

04:14.079 --> 04:17.613
stupid gross girlfriend Tiffy's a
vegan, and a... brother-stealer!

04:17.616 --> 04:20.084
Who can also
totally heeearyoooou...

04:20.086 --> 04:22.119
Which is amazing
because why aren't you dead

04:22.120 --> 04:23.187
from protein deficiency?!

04:23.189 --> 04:25.890
Uh, because I get all
eight essential amino acids

04:25.892 --> 04:30.194
from amaranth and quinoa without
murdering helpless animals?

04:30.196 --> 04:30.928
Oooooh!

04:30.930 --> 04:31.829
kkkuughh!

04:31.831 --> 04:33.298
Hey, Tiff?

04:33.300 --> 04:36.968
Could you, instead of antagonizing
her, maybe go ahead and take off?

04:36.970 --> 04:40.506
Love yoooou.

04:40.508 --> 04:44.043
We'll rendezvous with my research vessel
in a few hours, so in the meantime,

04:44.045 --> 04:47.880
I guess, continue to make such
wildly liberal use of the bar.

04:47.882 --> 04:52.384
Done! You're okay, Cecil. I
don't get why Cheryl hates you so much.

04:52.386 --> 04:52.918
Right?

04:52.920 --> 04:55.021
I mean, you've got
this whole Jacques Cousteau-

04:55.023 --> 04:58.291
- thing going on, that's-
- Just one of many philanthropies. I have so

04:58.293 --> 04:59.826
much on my plate, as it were.

04:59.828 --> 05:03.898
Children Without Plates, speaking of
plates, uh, Doctors Within Borders...

05:03.900 --> 05:04.999
Within borders.

05:05.001 --> 05:06.834
Well, of countries
ravaged by war.

05:06.836 --> 05:09.937
Right, otherwise-
Otherwise there's not really much point.

05:09.939 --> 05:14.842
Then there's Nourish A Child, Shoe
A Child, Bespectacle A Child,

05:14.844 --> 05:18.612
- umm, One Laptop Per Child Soldier...
- Wait, what?

05:18.614 --> 05:22.283
Which, unfortunately, soon became
One Thousand Laptops Per Warlord.

05:22.285 --> 05:24.785
Man, all those charities
have gotta cost, like -

05:24.787 --> 05:26.921
Hey! I should
go help Tiffy.

05:26.923 --> 05:32.293
Since we're flying into the Bermuda Triangle...
where mysteries abound!

05:32.295 --> 05:33.995
What kind of mysteries?

05:33.997 --> 05:37.265
I'm kidding!

05:37.267 --> 05:39.467
Well Cheryl,
you come by it honest.

05:39.469 --> 05:41.369
- Speaking of...
- Aagh! Lana c'mon,

05:41.371 --> 05:43.171
we're about to fly into the
Bermuda Triangle, my nerves

05:43.173 --> 05:44.673
are frayed enough as it is.

05:44.675 --> 05:45.540
Really.

05:45.542 --> 05:47.976
No, Long Island Iced
Tea number three really took

05:47.978 --> 05:48.977
the edge off. Want one?

05:48.979 --> 05:53.848
No, I'm not drinking, but-
Oh my God! I totally saw this coming!

05:53.850 --> 05:54.816
You saw what coming?

05:54.818 --> 05:56.885
Did you not join
the Nation of Islam?

05:56.887 --> 05:57.919
No, Archer, I -

05:57.921 --> 05:58.687
You know they won't

05:58.689 --> 05:59.655
let you keep dating Cyril,

05:59.657 --> 06:00.989
right? Plus no bacon?

06:00.991 --> 06:02.624
You done?

06:02.626 --> 06:05.694
Well for now, but after I take a nap-
You'll wake up just in

06:05.696 --> 06:08.597
time to get shot for treason, because
your mother wants to ransom a hydrogen

06:08.599 --> 06:10.332
bomb back to the United
States government.

06:10.334 --> 06:14.837
It's a reward! And maritime
salvage law is very clear on the subject.

06:14.839 --> 06:16.605
According to Cecil.

06:16.607 --> 06:17.974
And what's he
getting out of this?

06:17.976 --> 06:21.477
I... guess whatever useless
thing philanthropists normally get from

06:21.479 --> 06:23.380
squandering their
money on the poor.

06:23.382 --> 06:27.317
So what, he's conducting a huge
naval operation just for a warm fuzzy?

06:27.319 --> 06:29.319
I -- hey, wait a second!

06:29.321 --> 06:30.220
What?

06:30.222 --> 06:33.023
I think I have
room for a fuzzy navel.

06:33.025 --> 06:36.059
Wow Tiffy,
who taught you how to fly?

06:36.061 --> 06:38.828
Was it that goose you freed,
ruining last year's Christmas

06:38.830 --> 06:42.432
dinner, or --
Rrrgh, Cecil, I swear to Goddess...?

06:42.434 --> 06:46.103
I know, Tiffy, but please, try
to focus on the greater good. In the

06:46.105 --> 06:48.939
words of the immortal Jeremy Bentham-
Good thing I'm

06:48.941 --> 06:52.009
immortal, cause if she says one
more word to me I will slam

06:52.011 --> 06:55.045
this helicopter into
the frickin ocean.

06:55.047 --> 06:58.882
Well, you seem busy.

06:58.884 --> 07:04.120
So say it's worth two billion,
a fair reward on that would be...

07:04.122 --> 07:05.488
um, hello!

07:05.490 --> 07:08.491
Oh, Mr. Tunt! Please,
join me, you're just the person

07:08.493 --> 07:11.528
- I want to talk to...
- And I you. About my

07:11.530 --> 07:14.498
sister. I was curious if
you'd noticed anything...

07:14.500 --> 07:16.667
well, curious, about
her behavior.

07:16.669 --> 07:18.602
Ha! Ha! Ha!

07:18.604 --> 07:19.969
Oh, you're serious.

07:19.971 --> 07:21.638
I'm afraid so, yes.

07:21.640 --> 07:23.807
Well how much
time do you have?

07:23.809 --> 07:31.081
- As much as you need...
- Oh my God, I

07:31.083 --> 07:35.451
don't know what to say... I have
figuratively lost my tongue.

07:35.453 --> 07:37.854
With Brent it
was almost literally.

07:37.856 --> 07:39.622
That's why we can't
have scissors.

07:39.624 --> 07:42.925
I had no idea her mental state
had declined to such an extent. I mean,

07:42.927 --> 07:47.063
- the arson's not surprising...
- What have you done?

07:47.065 --> 07:47.897
Ha haha!

07:47.899 --> 07:49.732
Take that, gazebo!

07:49.734 --> 07:52.002
But you're
telling me she had...

07:52.004 --> 07:54.905
Mm! Choke-sex,
that's her kink!

07:54.907 --> 07:58.877
With a KGB cyborg. After she led him
straight to the ISIS safehouse,

07:58.879 --> 08:01.680
at 921 East
Seventy-Third Street.

08:01.682 --> 08:04.449
Oh my -- wait,
is that classified?

08:04.451 --> 08:07.853
- I won't tell if you won't tell...
- Mmmkay! Well, I

08:07.855 --> 08:11.957
appreciate your candor in this matter, Ms. Archer-
Oh no, it's Ms.

08:11.959 --> 08:13.081
Oh.

08:13.201 --> 08:18.086
Ms., yes, thank
you for, um... yes.

08:27.359 --> 08:29.594
Come on, you
call this fully stocked?

08:29.596 --> 08:32.330
And no Georgia peaches?
What the--?

08:32.332 --> 08:33.231
What're you doing?

08:33.232 --> 08:35.131
I --
what're you doing?!

08:35.134 --> 08:38.102
Hairy navel. Started
as a fuzzy, but I'm calling

08:38.104 --> 08:42.873
this vacation, so... Okay.

08:42.875 --> 08:45.109
Love our little talks!

08:45.111 --> 08:46.677
Rrowrf. Nom nom nomnomnom.

08:46.679 --> 08:48.379
Hi, it's Pam, right?

08:48.381 --> 08:51.215
Enjoying the cruelty-free
vegan seafood buffet?

08:51.217 --> 08:54.885
Mrmff, it's pretty good, once you
get over how allergic I am to soy.

08:54.887 --> 08:56.454
What?! Oh my
God, don't eat that!

08:56.456 --> 08:58.890
Wh-? Hey! I am
a consenting adult.

08:58.892 --> 09:03.695
Plus I assume you've got an epi-pen
on this big Riptide-lookin' bastard?

09:03.697 --> 09:07.131
I -- yes, in the first
aid kit in the cockpit, but -

09:07.133 --> 09:08.900
Well then shut up.

09:08.902 --> 09:15.173
Shutting up, yes. But before I do, could I...
ask you a few questions?

09:15.175 --> 09:17.841
How is everybody
okay with this?

09:17.843 --> 09:18.675
How are you not?

09:18.677 --> 09:19.376
Lana, you heard Ms.

09:19.378 --> 09:21.378
Archer, it's either us
or the Russians, and -

09:21.380 --> 09:24.214
I did not hear that, actually, but-
But if you found

09:24.216 --> 09:26.984
somebody's wallet, you'd
expect to get a reward, so -

09:26.986 --> 09:28.552
What if they
won't pay a reward?

09:28.554 --> 09:30.120
Then what, she just
keeps the bomb?

09:30.122 --> 09:31.488
C'mon, it's not
gonna come to that.

09:31.490 --> 09:33.624
Ooh, but if it does
we could move to Cecil's island

09:33.626 --> 09:35.058
and be a rogue state!

09:35.060 --> 09:37.661
- Coool...
- Ugh, forget it.

09:37.663 --> 09:42.165
Oh, and also dummies? We're five
hundred miles from the nearest tree.

09:42.167 --> 09:44.835
Hey thanks, Magellan!

09:44.837 --> 09:47.538
Hey wait, why the heck are you
painting my face like this?!

09:47.540 --> 09:49.073
Cause you look fierce.

09:49.075 --> 09:50.074
Rrowr.

09:50.076 --> 09:51.209
Rrowrf.

09:51.211 --> 09:53.077
Well thank you, Pam,
I appreciate your candor,

09:53.079 --> 09:57.215
and -- you really, really should
really stop eating those.

09:57.217 --> 09:58.583
Last one.

09:58.585 --> 10:02.119
Mmrowmf.

10:02.121 --> 10:05.155
Malory, please, is there any way
I can get you to reconsider this?

10:05.157 --> 10:08.925
- Well, if you feel that strongly...
- I so do.

10:08.927 --> 10:12.662
Cecil says marine salvage goes
for ten to twenty percent of the item's

10:12.664 --> 10:16.600
value, but since all I'm asking is a
measly three percent, if you've got

10:16.602 --> 10:19.302
sixty million dollars
lying around...?

10:19.304 --> 10:20.303
Bwexqueeze me?!

10:20.305 --> 10:21.604
I know, right?

10:21.606 --> 10:23.506
It's a steal at twice the price.

10:23.508 --> 10:27.111
Yeah and about that, Cyril
figured out how big our bonuses should be.

10:27.113 --> 10:28.212
Your what?!

10:28.214 --> 10:29.380
I -- Ray made me!

10:29.382 --> 10:31.783
Cyril! C'mon
you're fierce, rrowr!

10:31.785 --> 10:34.319
Rrraarrgh!

10:34.321 --> 10:36.654
No! Don't!

10:37.557 --> 10:39.090
Uh, could I speak
to you for a moment?

10:39.092 --> 10:40.525
"Wildly liberal use,"

10:40.527 --> 10:43.261
Cecil, those were
your exact words!

10:43.263 --> 10:46.698
No, of course, that's totally fine,
but I wanted to talk to you about -

10:46.700 --> 10:49.167
Don't say high-
functioning alcoholism.

10:49.169 --> 10:51.202
I wasn't. Going to.

10:51.204 --> 10:52.269
Well then
what's on your mind?

10:52.271 --> 10:55.873
- Well, it's about my sister...
- Hey whoa! I dunno what

10:55.875 --> 10:59.343
she told you but Carol's a consenting adult, so-
Well that's actually

10:59.345 --> 11:01.711
kind of my point, I wanted
to ask if you'd ever

11:01.713 --> 11:09.052
seen my sister acting strangely, or-
Ha! Oh, you're serious.

11:13.192 --> 11:18.128
Just ignore
it, it's non-diegetic.

11:18.130 --> 11:20.631
Last one,
stinky-pinky-swear.

11:20.633 --> 11:21.865
Mrowf.

11:21.867 --> 11:22.866
Psst! Pam!

11:22.868 --> 11:24.969
Aw crap, already?

11:24.971 --> 11:25.636
Pam!

11:25.638 --> 11:29.673
Look, auditory hallucinations aren't
gonna make you any less delicious.

11:29.675 --> 11:32.109
Hey! I was talking to that!

11:32.111 --> 11:33.377
Shhh! Shut up!
I need your help!

11:33.379 --> 11:34.612
And that's how you ask?

11:34.614 --> 11:36.280
Cecil's like,
interviewing everybody!

11:36.282 --> 11:38.849
Yeah, he -- is he?
Doing that?

11:38.851 --> 11:40.151
Yes! And I
think he's taping it!

11:40.153 --> 11:41.986
Look, there's
cameras everywhere!

11:41.988 --> 11:43.187
Huh.

11:43.189 --> 11:44.755
I think he's
taping them saying I'm crazy

11:44.757 --> 11:47.825
so he can show it to a judge and
get a conservatorship over me!

11:47.827 --> 11:49.493
Huh.

11:49.495 --> 11:50.860
"Huh" what?!

11:50.862 --> 11:54.864
I mean... ya think that's
the worst idea anybody ever had?

11:54.866 --> 11:56.366
Oh. My God.

11:56.368 --> 11:58.635
I know, it's hard to hear, but-

11:58.637 --> 11:59.369
Owww!

11:59.371 --> 12:00.537
I thought
you were my friend!

12:00.539 --> 12:04.742
Yeah and for like six months you
also thought you were a werewolf!

12:04.744 --> 12:08.045
Aw crap, I can't feel my face.

12:08.047 --> 12:13.452
Last one, swear to God.

12:13.454 --> 12:17.957
Swear to God, every full moon
she'd make us lock her in the ISIS vault.

12:17.959 --> 12:19.491
Oh my God, how
are you laughing?

12:19.493 --> 12:22.027
That's not funny, it's tragic!

12:22.029 --> 12:26.665
I -- no yeah, but you
know, plus time, it equals -

12:26.667 --> 12:28.601
Thank you, I've
heard quite enough.

12:28.603 --> 12:32.838
Now if you'll please excuse me, I-
Cecil? My darling whom I love?

12:32.840 --> 12:35.107
And also strangers
whom I don't even like?

12:35.109 --> 12:37.109
Our ETA is fifteen minutes.

12:37.111 --> 12:42.181
And the seas are really choppy, so
we may be in for a rough landing.

12:42.183 --> 12:45.051
Thank you love yoooooou.

12:45.053 --> 12:48.521
So you may want to
switch to coffee.

12:48.523 --> 12:51.158
Ha! Ha! Ha! Ahhh.

12:51.160 --> 12:54.093
Oh, you're still serious.

12:54.095 --> 12:57.530
Or am I?

12:57.532 --> 12:59.566
I am, actually.

12:59.568 --> 13:01.768
Have you people
lost your minds?!

13:01.770 --> 13:04.671
- 'cause apparently it's going around...
- Because - shut up - if

13:04.673 --> 13:09.676
we recover the bomb, I will decide if
any of you receives a tiny bonus, so -

13:09.678 --> 13:10.778
If?! If?!

13:10.780 --> 13:12.312
Guys, shut up,
I got this, shut up.

13:12.314 --> 13:13.614
What do you mean, if?!

13:13.616 --> 13:15.016
Also, what are we talking about?

13:15.018 --> 13:19.854
Nothing. There's nothing to talk
about, because I am -- Jesus Christ!

13:19.856 --> 13:22.190
Okay, it's either
the altitude or a stroke.

13:22.192 --> 13:25.294
Mother, it's Sterling!
Do you smell toast?

13:25.296 --> 13:26.095
Pam?!

13:26.097 --> 13:30.700
Grrrgh, grrrgh!

13:30.702 --> 13:33.336
What the-
-- hell are you doing?!

13:33.338 --> 13:35.572
The cockpit is off
limits, missy!

13:35.574 --> 13:38.742
Oh yeah?!
Well so's my inheritance!

13:39.611 --> 13:42.612
Goddammit, shut
up John Williams!

13:42.614 --> 13:45.148
Oh my God you
really are crazy!

13:45.150 --> 13:47.116
Would a crazy person do this?!

